name: Miller Walker
description: I am a really fun person who loves people, loves to laugh, I am very caring,love music, dancing, singing ( in my car) ! Love the church…I am a devoted friend. I like to have fun,I have strong moral values with honesty and integrity being the core of my personality, am very cool, i respect my dignity….I’m excited to see new places, meet new people and do new things.I’m not a fighter and I don’t argue, life’s too short but I do value friendship and intimacy…
